## Message Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant REPL
    participant State
    participant Query
    participant API
    participant Tools
    participant UI
    
    User->>REPL: Input
    REPL->>State: Update messages
    State-->>Query: Trigger query
    
    Query->>Query: Build context
    
    loop Until Complete
        Query->>API: Stream request
        API-->>Query: Stream events
        
        alt Text Event
            Query->>UI: text delta
        end
        
        alt Tool Call
            Query->>Tools: Execute tool
            Tools-->>Query: Result
            Query->>API: Continue request
        end
    end
    
    Query-->>State: Complete
    State-->>UI: Update display
    UI-->>User: Show response
```

## Tool Execution Pipeline

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    subgraph DETECT["1. Detection"]
        D_STREAM["Stream Response"]
        D_PARSE["Parse Event"]
        D_TOOL["ToolUseBlock"]
    end
    
    subgraph PERM["2. Permission"]
        P_CHECK["Check canUseTool"]
        P_STATE["Permission State"]
        P_ASK{"Approved?"}
    end
    
    subgraph EXEC["3. Execution"]
        E_FIND["findTool"]
        E_PART["Partition Safety"]
        E_PARALLEL["Parallel (Read-only)"]
        E_SERIAL["Serial (Stateful)"]
        E_PROGRESS["Stream Progress"]
    end
    
    subgraph RESULT["4. Result"]
        R_FORMAT["Format Result"]
        R_ADD["Add to Messages"]
        R_LOOP{"More Tools?"}
        R_EXIT["Continue"]
    end
    
    D_STREAM --> D_PARSE --> D_TOOL
    D_TOOL --> P_CHECK --> P_STATE --> P_ASK
    P_ASK -->|Yes| E_FIND
    P_ASK -->|No| R_FORMAT
    E_FIND --> E_PART --> E_PARALLEL
    E_PART --> E_SERIAL
    E_PARALLEL --> E_PROGRESS
    E_SERIAL --> E_PROGRESS --> R_FORMAT
    R_FORMAT --> R_ADD --> R_LOOP
    R_LOOP -->|Yes| D_STREAM
    R_LOOP -->|No| R_EXIT
```

