## Compaction Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Query
    participant Compact
    participant API
    participant Store
    
    Query->>Query: Check token count
    
    alt Token limit approaching
        Query->>Compact: Trigger compaction
        
        Compact->>Store: Get all messages
        Store-->>Compact: messages
        
        Compact->>Compact: Find boundary
        
        Note right of Compact: Skip recent messages<br/>Skip tool results
        
        Compact->>Compact: Extract older messages
        
        Compact->>API: Summarize request
        API-->>Compact: summary text
        
        Compact->>Compact: Create boundary message
        Compact->>Store: Replace with summary
        Store-->>Query: Compacted messages
        
        Query->>Query: Continue query
    end
```

