## Session Lifecycle

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Init
    
    Init --> Loading: Parse args
    Loading --> Configured: Load settings
    Configured --> Auth: Setup auth
    Auth --> MCP: Connect servers
    MCP --> Ready: All ready
    
    Ready --> Query: User input
    Query --> Tools: Tool call
    Tools --> Query: Result
    Query --> Ready: Complete
    
    Ready --> Compact: Context full
    Compact --> Query: Resume
    
    Query --> Error: API error
    Error --> Retry: Backoff
    Retry --> Query: Retry
    Retry --> Fail: Give up
    
    Ready --> [*]: /exit
    Fail --> [*]
```

